      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画了c1--|Yes| c2和c1--|No| c6两条分支。c6也是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine类型对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
